{"tid":1217200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整合下一次所需物資","createTime":"2019-06-13T12:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T10:47:11.000Z","uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"24ac2703c10e7f51a4e4a16f98d8d8b21bdd9c52","tid":1217200,"uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:20:05.000Z","msg":"經過尋日大家都大概知道邊啲物資係需要邊啲係次要<br />\n<br />\n趁有時間先搞好補給，再諗埋補給方法同路線<br />\n<br />\n物資需要應該以solution-focused 嘅角度嚟考慮<br />\n<br />\n簡單比喻，你出剪，我一係出剪或者揼，至於係剪係揼，視乎物資準備嘅難度/成本或其他考慮<br />\n<br />\n先拋磚引玉<br />\n蒸溜水 - 無限量供應<br />\n1) 整熄任何燃燒嘅嘢<br />\n2) 作為生理鹽水嘅替代品<br />\n3) 飲用<br />\n<br />\n呢個post 需要大家嘅力量整合咁咁多位先可以準備到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0540156b8a18c1b92c8483e778c7a7864c0ea137","tid":1217200,"uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:35:41.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"25056a84b36681fa0de6d70e15806ad858b13541","tid":1217200,"uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8362f0fef15e211f2e840ea4eccec9af8c4b8b0","tid":1217200,"uid":124156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d5ca28a5f45599c2d9630328fdae75a8732cd6","tid":1217200,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得<br />\n<br />\n早幾日 連粉嶺屯門 未出發物資都比狗搞<br />\n點解唔可以學水貨客咁螞蟻搬家<